Team Member Workflow
Every member logs in and lands in My Workspace.
Their dashboard answers:
"What should I work on today?"
They can see:
My assigned features
My sprint
My deliverables
My meetings
My daily update
My pending reviews
Recent activity
Nothing more.
They don't need to navigate through the whole system.

Project Manager Workflow
The Project Manager sees the complete picture.
They can:
Create projects
Build the roadmap
Create modules
Create features
Create sprints
Assign team members
Schedule meetings
Review deliverables
Approve completed work
Monitor blockers
Track project progress
They are managing outcomes rather than chasing updates.


